#Fake Data Generator
This website is a simple website to generate fake personal data.

## Personal data generators:
- Swiss IBAN number.


## Website
- Single page for now with a simple UI. Single button to generate a new IBAN number and display it on the page, as well as the account number.

## TECH STACK
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- React.js

## Hosting
It is hosted on affinityfree.com, which is a free hosting service. (Only support javascript on the client side, so no backend code can be used.)